app_details.title: Injector Origin
app_details.description: Injector Origin is more than just an injector app. Dive into our hero guides, packed with valuable tips and tricks to master every hero's abilities and strategies. Elevate your skills and enhance your gaming experience with Injector Origin now!

reviews.content: I really recommend this injector because it's so very convenient and easy to use. 4 stars because not like Lesley Aspirants and Lunox Legend skin is full voice line but why Kagura's Beyond The Clouds and Exorcist skin are not full voice line? I will give this 5 stars if they add or make it a whole voice line to those skin but for now it's 4/5. I hope you add more voice line to those skins I mentioned Thankyou and god bless 😊🥰
reviews.replyContent:
Thanks for the feedback! We're glad you like the injector.
We wanted to let you know that due to the latest MLBB update, some skins may not work correctly with the injector at this time. We're working hard to resolve this issue and appreciate your patience.
Thanks for the great review! We're glad you're enjoying the app. 🙌
